channel.title: This is dumb. Help me move everyone away from 317 servers
channel.description:
PLEASE check your old pc's/pc backups for a RuneScape caches, which when you right click - properties says a date between those: 18-Jun-2007 - 06-Aug-2007. And upload and pm/post it here. I'll create a server for it, and the person providing the cache decides whenever I can release or not.
The caches can be found if you go into "My Computer", then into the C:/ drive, or the "Local disk" drive, then find a folder called ".jagex_cache_32", go into it, into runescape, and right click the main_file_cache.idx2, to check the date.
When you upload the cache, find the folder ".jages_cache_32" again, and right click it - add to ".jagex_cache_32.rar", and upload it here: [URL=http://"http://uppit.com"]http://uppit.com[/URL]
If it does not say anything aobut add to ".jagex_cache_32.rar", when download and install winrar here: [URL=http://"http://www.rarsoft.com/rar/wrar380.exe"]http://www.rarsoft.com/rar/wrar380.exe[/URL]
Help me achiving this, would you?
[IMG]http://i42.tinypic.com/2vs188w.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i44.tinypic.com/16ll4hw.jpg[/img]
Thanks alot! - Brown.
